  "wave_0_per_point": "masterspeed=30;\n\n//plot x,y over 50 samples, make spiral by adding t to angle\nn=sample*50;\nmyseed=.5*q8+time+sample;\nmyrand= sin(myseed)*100;\nbias=1; //if a is 0.1, bias=2; if a is 0.01, bias = 100; etc.\na= pow(myrand,bias);\n\nangle=sample*3.14159*100+myseed;\nx=.5+(cos(angle)*a);\ny=.5+(sin(angle)*a);\n\n//plot x,y over 50 samples, make spiral by adding t to angle\nn=sample*50;\nmyseed=.5*q8+time+sample;\n\nangle=sample*3.14159*100+myseed;\na=1;\nx=.5+(cos(angle)*a);\ny=.5+(sin(angle)*a);\n",
